CLUE - 1985

IMDb Rating: 7.1

  Six individuals Mr.Green(McKean), Mrs.Peacock(Brannen), Col.Mustard(Mull), Mrs.White(Kahn), Miss Scarlet(Warren), and Pro. Plum(Lloyd) have all received invitations to a mysterious house. They all have been invited to dinner and have no idea while they are there. When they reach the house they discover that the master is not home, but his butler Wadsworth(Curry) and Maid Yvette(Camp) are there. The guests are informed that they are there by the invitation of Mr.Boddy. Mr.Boddy is blackmailing them all and thats the only thing in common the six people have. Then people start dying in the home and now it&#039;s up to the whole group to see who is doing it and to see if they can get out alive.

Note: This is the first movie to have played in theaters with three different endings (depending on which theater you attended). You will see all three endings at the end of the movie.
